headline: Celsius upgraded to Overweight at Morgan Stanley on growth momentum
summary: Investing.com -- Morgan Stanley has upgraded Celsius Holdings to Overweight from Equal-weight, raising its price target to $70 from $61, citing improving sales momentum and stronger brand positioning.

headline: PepsiCo splashes into dirty soda with new Mountain Dew flavor
summary: Dirty Mountain Dew Cream Soda, set for a nationwide rollout next year, is one of the first efforts to bring the trend from restaurants to retail stores.
